OL,3,CThree Northern Ireland teaching unions
OL,4,Cvote to accept pay offer
OL,6,FThe offer will see the starting salary
OL,7,Ffor teachers in the region rise to
OL,8,F#30,000, equating to a 24.3% increase
OL,9,Fand making it equal to England.
OL,11,FThe proposal has been described as a
OL,12,Fcumulative total of 10.4% plus #1,000
OL,13,Fbeing applied to the other teachers'
OL,14,Fand leadership pay scales.
OL,16,FFive unions had agreed to suspend
OL,17,Fstrike action and consider the pay
OL,18,Foffer from Education Minister Paul
OL,19,FGivan.
