OL,6,FThe NASUWT union said will now
OL,7,Fconsider the results of the survey
OL,8,Fahead of a teachers' negotiating
OL,9,Fcommittee meeting on 26 March.
OL,11,F"Northern Ireland teachers are long
OL,12,Foverdue a pay award," said Dr Patrick
OL,13,FRoach from NASUWT.
OL,15,F"It is disgraceful that teachers have
OL,16,Fhad to wait for three years to receive
OL,17,Fa credible pay offer. Nevertheless,
OL,18,Fthe teaching profession deserves real
OL,19,Fterms pay restoration which must now
OL,20,Fbe a priority.
