OL,6,F"Pay is only one of our concerns for
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland's hard-working and
OL,8,Fdedicated teachers.
OL,10,F"The Department and employers must now
OL,11,Fdeliver on the commitments they have
OL,12,Fmade to tackle excessive workload if
OL,13,Fthey do not want action short of
OL,14,Fstrike to be a long term part of the
OL,15,Feducation landscape in schools."
OL,17,FJustin McCamphill from the NASUWT
OL,18,Fsaid: "Teachers deserve a decent pay
OL,19,Fincrease and should never have been
OL,20,Fforced to take to the streets to
OL,21,Fdemand it.
